apps.name: Odyssey
apps.subtitle: An alternative App Store for iOS.

Fast. Really Fast.
Odyssey is the first jailbreak to be written almost entirely in Swift.
 It's also a snappy, responsive experience that you can t find anywhere else, with full support for iOS 13.0-13.5 devices, including the latest iPads and iPhones.
